[10:24:57] Starting 'minify-js'...
[10:25:05] Finished 'minify-css' after 8.3 s
[10:25:05] Finished 'minify-js' after 8.49 s
[10:25:09] Finished 'minify-html' after 12 s
[10:25:09] Finished 'default' after 12 s

~~~

